Never use your hydrolyser in a medium or even partially enclosed or ventilated, make sure you use your hydrolyser in adequate conditions for renewing the air.

If pressure builds up in your hydrolyser the top of it ascend to himself and thus stop the production of gas. Make sure you never put constraints on the engagement of the security.

Never use fire source in the presence of your hydrolyser.

Never use a bubbler hydrolyser without security to evacuate gasses generated.

Never use electrical installation AC to power the electrodes (core) of your hydrolyser.

You are responsible for using your hydrolyser in all situations and in all places. Remember that water conducts electricity, do not spill your hydrolyser are functioning is only possible advantage of the effects of gravity, and therefore should be placed horizontally on a stable surface and clear of any possibility of destabilization drive a flow of water.

Do not let anyone access your hydrolyser when in operation. Be sure to store your hydrolyser to shelter people in risky behavior.

